$WmMEID_フレイヤ,ch00_27_Freya_F_Normal,Face_Smile|If the mortals draw closer to escape,
it will be your turn next. You do
understand, don't you, Plumeria?$k$pFinish them off. Put an end to your
old friends...$k$p$WmMEID_プルメリア,ch00_25_Plumeria_F_Normal,Face_Cool|Yes, Lady Freyja.$k$p$WmMEID_フレイヤ,ch00_27_Freya_F_Normal,Face_Anger|Fight, little álfar... Fight to the death.$k$pFeel the pain of lost love—the pain
I felt when my brother was taken
from me...$k$p$Sbs1000|

$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Cool2|...A-Alfonse?$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|You're awake! You had me worried,
fainting so suddenly...$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Cool2|Alfonse, I...$k$pI remember...so much.$k$pPlaying with friends in my dreams...$k$pBack when they were still...
Before they...$k$pWe played so many different
games...and had so much fun.$k$pWe pretended to go on adventures...
We wanted to save the world...$k$pOnly...I stayed behind...$k$pAnd, when we played dress-up...
When the two of us would trade
places when we woke up...$k$pAnna called that a...changeling...$k$p$EFace_Pain|Father, Mother... Brother...$k$pPapa... Sis!$k$pI...I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!
So, so sorry! So, so, so sorry!$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Pain|Sharena! Focus! What's happening?$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Pain|Alfonse, I—$k$pI might not be your sister.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Pain|...Are you serious?$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Pain|I'm trying to tell you... When I used
to play dress-up in my dreams...
I think we were being changelings.$k$pI have memories...of living
with another girl in a small,
crumbling house...$k$pSo, here's the truth: I might not
have also been Princess Sharena...$k$pI may have switched places with
her while dreaming... I don't know
how to know for sure.$k$pBut...I may have taken her place...$k$pAnd because of me... She...
The REAL Princess Sharena...
She, she...$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|Sharena, despite your memories,
that couldn't have happened.$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Pain|But...the house...and the other girl!$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|If what you say IS true, you two
traded places many times...$k$pSo, you—Sharena—would still have
memories from when you were
visiting that house, wouldn't you?$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Pain|...$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|I think we could use a little rest.
You take some time to yourself.
We'll head out soon.$k$p$WmMPID_シャロン,ch00_02_Sharon_F_Normal,Face_Pain|Alfonse...$k$p$Sbs1000|
